# Styles Context

When working with styles, refer to `documentation/architecture.md` for:
- SCSS is used for project styles with CSS custom properties (`--umo-*` prefix)
- TDesign vendor LESS bridge: `src/assets/styles/tdesign-vendor.less` (imported from `src/components/index.js`)
- TDesign overrides: `src/assets/styles/tdesign-overrides.scss`
- TDesign class prefix is overridden to `umo-` via `modifyVars` and `TConfigProvider`
- Main style entry: `src/assets/styles/index.scss`
- Editor content styles: `src/assets/styles/editor.scss`
- SVG icons use vite-plugin-svg-icons with `umo-icon-{name}` pattern
